The '''Financial Appropriations Committee''' of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] supervised, among other things, monetary grants issued by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] to various organizations and charities. It had a reputation for being stiff-necked.

[[Orn Free Taa/Legends|Orn Free Taa]] served on the Committee as of [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]]. In [[27 BBY/Legends|27 BBY]], it cut the proposed budget of the [[Outbound Flight Project]].

